Paul Mitchell
&nbsp;

This handsome boy came to us way back in 2010.&nbsp; He REALLY needs a home.&nbsp; We love him to death, but we'd be so very happy if he finally got a home!&nbsp; Paul is VERY playful and high energy.&nbsp; He loves to run and play, and can often be observed running around his yard having a great time.&nbsp; His potential adopter/family would have to be energetic, active people!&nbsp; Please don't let this handsome guy spend his entire life in a shelter.&nbsp; Fill out the adoption application below and bring home a handsome new friend!&nbsp;

My ideal home:
I'd love a very active, playful home!
I'm good with:

Older Children
&nbsp;
Men
&nbsp;
Women

I'm not good with:

Most Other Dogs
&nbsp;
