Sammie
&nbsp;
Hound Mix
&nbsp;
Birthdate: 2011
&nbsp;
Sammie is a bouncy loving boy. He&nbsp;has undergone balloon heart surgery for a malformed heart valve. His surgery was very sucessful and he is expected to live a normal life span. Sammie needs to take an inexpensive medication for the rest of his life. This boy is a miracle that is ready to bless a family with his love and excitement for life.
&nbsp;This fellow is full of personality and charm.

&nbsp;



***Please note the dogs in this picture are not in need of foster care or adoption, they are simply representative of the breed**




Merlin&rsquo;s Hope is always in need of committed foster&nbsp;parents who can give a rescued dog a&nbsp;temporary home and get it started on&nbsp;its way.&nbsp;Long-term and Short term homes are always needed.




If you have experience with the breed and are interested in offering a temporary home, and&nbsp;


